{
  "title": "Gourmet American Penne Pasta",
  "description": "A peppery and chewy American dish featuring penne pasta, this crowd-pleaser is made with a flambe technique and is ayurvedic-sattvic-friendly, cooked to perfection in a kadhai",
  "cuisine": "American",
